# Important point about artifacts

Because you are on **Azure DevOps Server / on-prem**, keep using **Build Artifacts**, not Pipeline Artifacts. Microsoft explicitly says Pipeline Artifact tasks are Azure DevOps Services-only, and Azure DevOps Server should use Build Artifact tasks instead. ([Microsoft Learn][3])

